{"tid":242713,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【RIP】今日係第二代黄蓉翁美玲第32年死忌","createTime":"2017-05-14T06:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T06:42:52.000Z","uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd73047c4f015753ea1332867b14f2ebf7e78ab","tid":242713,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:30:53.000Z","msg":"58歲死忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n翁美玲（英語：Barbara Yung Mei-ling，1959年5月7日－1985年5月14日），祖籍安徽，生於香港，1980年代初香港著名電視演員。1985年當時紅極一時的翁美玲突然自殺身亡，終年26歲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/141939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F141939_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d02682cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/142115_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F142115_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=5994aae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012年6月2日，翁美玲的前荷蘭男友羅泊&middot;萊得鮑（Rob Radboud）幫美玲製作網站 並公開美玲回港發展前的珍貴照片和交往時的故事。<br />\n<br />\n部份文章有好多fans幫手翻譯咗做中文<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.barbarayung.nl/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.barbarayung.nl%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=3d4aedc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.barbarayung.nl/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，翁美玲的母親於2017年1月17日在英國逝世，享年91歲。於2017年2月23日在當地舉殯及火化，與翁美玲合葬於劍橋公墓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/142455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F142455_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=30cc98cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在翁美玲自殺前兩星期，她到美容院找鄭明明，當時充滿心事，打算找她詳談，剛巧鄭明明當日有數項重要公事正須解決，自己正忙得一塌糊塗，便很敷衍地表示工作很忙，改天大家比較空閒才坐下詳談，兩個星期後，翁美玲便自殺身亡。<br />\n翁美玲的死，導致藝人的心靈需要備受關注，最終促成香港首個專為服事藝人的基督教團體藝人之家的成立。<br />\n<br />\n2000年代有廣播節目主持信口雌黃將發生於1976年10月5日偉錦園7樓D座職業殺手殺人後棄屍浴缸命案與翁美玲自殺拉上關係，說成是同一單位，但翁美玲自殺單位是偉錦園1樓1B座，殺人案單位是7樓D座。<br />\n<br />\n2005年有大陸網民杜撰漏洞頗多的文章惡意攻擊藝人沈殿霞，將沈殿霞與翁美玲自殺拉上關係。<br />\n<br />\n翁美玲逝世後也有不少靈異傳聞；有傳翁的好友﹑影迷都見過翁的鬼魂。其中一名影迷更表示翁曾經報夢給她解釋其自殺的真相，實為本來只想嚇唬一下身邊的男友，怎料弄假成真，返魂乏術。根據新聞報道翁的屍體在客廳被發現時正俯臥，推測她感到辛苦欲前往大門，可惜不支倒地。此靈異傳聞當然不能證實，而影迷對翁的早逝只能永遠地感到惋惜﹑傷感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/142714_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F142714_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f89a0a1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90c0911a422a7946d9f35522f6d04f2318036b67","tid":242713,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"黃蓉笑道：&ldquo;也不怕羞！原來咱倆夫妻和順，只因爲你武功勝過我了。郭大俠，來來來，咱倆比劃比劃。&rdquo;<br />\n郭靖笑道：&ldquo;好，黃幫主，你劃下道兒來罷。&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/143144_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F143144_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d3e79fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/143207_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F143207_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=10ef2a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2672b4eda9230d12e8d7cdd8f1b11c0624273953","tid":242713,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/89329/-翁美玲生忌-黃蓉形象深入民心-新射鵰明天首播令人懷念-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F89329%2F-%E7%BF%81%E7%BE%8E%E7%8E%B2%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%8C-%E9%BB%83%E8%93%89%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%B7%B1%E5%85%A5%E6%B0%91%E5%BF%83-%E6%96%B0%E5%B0%84%E9%B5%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%A4%A9%E9%A6%96%E6%92%AD%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E6%87%B7%E5%BF%B5-&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=28033c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/娛樂/89329/-翁美玲生忌-黃蓉形象深入民心-新射鵰明天首播令人懷念-</a><br />\n<br />\n【永遠的黃蓉】逝世32年 翁美玲母離世 將合葬劍橋墓園 (18:20)<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170221/s00007/1487672579705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170221%2Fs00007%2F1487672579705&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7b41e8bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170221%2Fs00007%2F1487672579705&h=15c30545\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170221/s00007/1487672579705</a><br />\n<br />\n歷代黃蓉：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hk2W09i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhk2W09i.jpg&h=8f526f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【射鵰英雄傳】新黃蓉李一桐可愛煞食　懷念翁美玲美得心碎<br />\n<br />\n金庸名著《射鵰英雄傳》拍過無數版本，而每次開拍觀眾最關心的除了劇情有否大改動外，飾演黃蓉的人選，更是劇集成功與否的關鍵，但內地版的《射鵰英雄傳2017》，卻大膽起用新人李一桐，究竟她是如何脫穎而出，而多年來演過黃蓉的女星便有米雪、翁美玲、朱茵、周迅及林依晨，網民又最喜愛哪一位呢？李一桐又能否力壓前輩，在網民心中留下印象。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/69809/-%E5%B0%84%E9%B5%B0%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%82%B3-%E6%96%B0%E9%BB%83%E8%93%89%E6%9D%8E%E4%B8%80%E6%A1%90%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E7%85%9E%E9%A3%9F-%E6%87%B7%E5%BF%B5%E7%BF%81%E7%BE%8E%E7%8E%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%8E?utm_content=buffer60503&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F69809%2F-%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25B5%25B0%25E8%258B%25B1%25E9%259B%2584%25E5%2582%25B3-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25BB%2583%25E8%2593%2589%25E6%259D%258E%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A1%2590%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2585%259E%25E9%25A3%259F-%25E6%2587%25B7%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E7%25BF%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%258E%25B2%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A2%258E%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer60503%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=52e5824f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/69809/-%E5%B0%84%E9%B5%B0%E8%8B%B1%E9%9B%84%E5%82%B3-%E6%96%B0%E9%BB%83%E8%93%89%E6%9D%8E%E4%B8%80%E6%A1%90%E5%8F%AF%E6%84%9B%E7%85%9E%E9%A3%9F-%E6%87%B7%E5%BF%B5%E7%BF%81%E7%BE%8E%E7%8E%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%BE%97%E5%BF%83%E7%A2%8E?utm_content=buffer60503&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a>"}]}